{"parentUuid":"1013c251-bea9-4348-a2f1-bd2b96b9fc96","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a1f81fe877b9073d0","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MteuXuZW4xXpB65jhZ3JDM","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Jagat Kalyan Proof Lattice\n     2→\n     3→- Generated: 2026-03-14T15:34:52.125531+00:00\n     4→- Overall readiness: GREEN (0.84)\n     5→- Strongest layer: `moral`\n     6→- Weakest layer: `institutional`\n     7→- Benchmark portfolio: 30 project rows / 8 worker profiles\n     8→\n     9→## Layers\n    10→\n    11→### Mathematical credibility\n    12→- Score: GREEN (0.80)\n    13→- Artifacts:\n    14→  - WELFARE_TONS_SPEC.md\n    15→  - welfare_tons.py\n    16→  - 6 test functions across tests/\n    17→  - Sensitivity + budget optimizer support\n    18→- Gaps:\n    19→  - Increase formal test coverage\n    20→\n    21→### Empirical credibility\n    22→- Score: GREEN (1.00)\n    23→- Artifacts:\n    24→  - 30 public benchmark rows\n    25→  - 8 worker transition profiles\n    26→  - Strategy comparison benchmark\n    27→  - Grant + partner research documents\n    28→- Gaps:\n    29→  - Replace synthetic benchmark notes with 10 fully sourced real-world rows\n    30→\n    31→### Technical credibility\n    32→- Score: GREEN (1.00)\n    33→- Artifacts:\n    34→  - FastAPI app and SQLAlchemy data model\n    35→  - Claude-assisted matcher + heuristic fallback\n    36→  - Deterministic proof lattice generator\n    37→  - Machine-readable state + shared markdown outputs\n    38→- Gaps:\n    39→  - Expose benchmark and proof-lattice outputs via API or export endpoint\n    40→\n    41→### Moral credibility\n    42→- Score: GREEN (1.00)\n    43→- Artifacts:\n    44→  - 10 explicit guardrails\n    45→  - Multiplicative zero-kills-all enforcement\n    46→  - Agency + verification decomposition\n    47→  - Budget benchmark against carbon-only and jobs-only baselines\n    48→- Gaps:\n    49→  - Add a reviewer-facing checklist mapping each guardrail to one failure example\n    50→\n    51→### Institutional credibility\n    52→- Score: RED (0.40)\n    53→- Artifacts:\n    54→  - 12 stakeholder targets across 6 categories\n    55→  - Evidence goals per target\n    56→  - Autonomous requirements tracker\n    57→- Gaps:\n    58→  - Move at least 3 stakeholder targets to interviewed status with notes.\n    59→  - Secure 2 letters of interest or pilot-review signals.\n    60→  - Log more evidence notes from conversations and reviews."}]},"uuid":"f50422b6-93e6-4761-8737-9b5829753b41","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:17:36.021Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"1013c251-bea9-4348-a2f1-bd2b96b9fc96","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
